# --- Default owner for everything ---
*                        @and3rn3t

# --- Documentation ---
# *.md                     @your-org/docs-team
# docs/                    @your-org/docs-team

# --- CI/CD and DevOps ---
# .github/                 @your-org/devops
# .github/workflows/       @your-org/devops

# --- Frontend ---
# src/components/          @your-org/frontend
# src/pages/               @your-org/frontend
# *.css                    @your-org/frontend

# --- Backend / API ---
# src/api/                 @your-org/backend
# src/services/            @your-org/backend

# --- Database ---
# migrations/              @your-org/backend @your-org/dba
# src/models/              @your-org/backend

# --- Security-sensitive files ---
# src/auth/                @your-org/security
# SECURITY.md              @your-org/security
